\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 \
This test script generates a quick 10-second video sample (300 frames) using a simplified schematic grid. Instead of using real artwork, it uses colored geometric blocks built exactly to your real-world dimensions.\
Running this script allows you to verify that the guard's feet stay locked to the floor line, the storefront ads align perfectly inside the walls, and the guard walks 
